  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5 \u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Action taken to arrest person walking around with President's official flag on his waist",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police have launched investigations to arrest a man who carried the official flag of the President during the recent public protest in Colombo.",
        "A video shared on social media shows the man lying in bed using the official flag of the president as a blanket.",
        "The person who carried the flag after the public besieged the President's office in Colombo on July 09 has been identified through CCTV footage, police said.",
        "The police said that the suspect could be seen walking around with the flag tied around his waist and have started investigations based on the CCTV evidence."
      ],
